The structure of the site is such that we have different sections for each navigation item:
- /parent
- /school
- /ppozo
- /company
All underlying pages start with the same path.
So we can change the look of the navigation, based on the section you are in.

And also  for 
- /about
- /faq

This is the code to do so:
<script>
  $(document).ready(function () {
    const path = window.location.pathname;
    
    if (path.startsWith("/section1/")) {
      $("#nav-section1").addClass("active");
    } else if (path.startsWith("/section2/")) {
      $("#nav-section2").addClass("active");
    }
    // Add more conditions as per your sections
  });
</script>

